After what happened today,

5
00:01:49,150 --> 00:01:51,750
I've come to
understand Luan'er's character.

6
00:01:51,830 --> 00:01:53,430
Regarding your marriage...

7
00:01:54,180 --> 00:01:57,039
Madam, it's not what you think.

8
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:58,680
I was out of my mind today

9
00:01:58,710 --> 00:02:00,310
and hired someone to pose as a robber,

10
00:02:00,310 --> 00:02:01,840
just to gain your approval.

11
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:04,520
But somehow,

12
00:02:04,700 --> 00:02:05,850
my plan backfired

13
00:02:05,950 --> 00:02:08,780
and nearly cost you
and Shaoheng your lives.

14
00:02:09,210 --> 00:02:12,150
I know I've betrayed your trust.

15
00:02:16,180 --> 00:02:19,240
I dare not mention
my marriage to Shaoheng anymore

16
00:02:19,490 --> 00:02:21,690
I only ask for your forgiveness, Madam.

17
00:02:26,010 --> 00:02:26,640
Come.

18
00:02:29,230 --> 00:02:31,240
Luan'er, don't talk nonsense.

19
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,760
Those assassins today were ruthless.

20
00:02:33,930 --> 00:02:35,100
They nearly took your life.

21
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:37,100
How could they possibly be hired by you?

22
00:02:37,100 --> 00:02:38,560
Those four who escaped

23
00:02:38,620 --> 00:02:40,090
were probably hired by her,

24
00:02:40,090 --> 00:02:41,550
but those who tried
to kill us mother and son

25
00:02:41,550 --> 00:02:43,570
have absolutely nothing to do with her.

26
00:02:43,570 --> 00:02:44,579
Madam.

27
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:45,950
Shaoheng.

28
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:48,450
You insisted I go burn incense,

29
00:02:48,690 --> 00:02:51,020
and things were strange all along the way.

30
00:02:51,170 --> 00:02:53,510
I bet you had a hand in this too.

31
