Luan'er is injured now,

33
00:02:59,490 --> 00:03:00,460
and in the future,

34
00:03:00,460 --> 00:03:03,180
she probably can't
carry water or brew tea.

35
00:03:03,340 --> 00:03:06,010
I think we might as well
close the teahouse.

36
00:03:06,970 --> 00:03:09,620
Mother, how can you say such things?

37
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:11,970
Luan'er was injured trying to save you...

38
00:03:12,020 --> 00:03:13,450
This is all my own fault.

39
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:14,540
I blame no one else.

40
00:03:14,670 --> 00:03:16,200
Please don't worry, Madam.

41
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:22,800
My son may be a bit of a scoundrel,

42
00:03:22,890 --> 00:03:24,750
but he still has some conscience.

43
00:03:25,079 --> 00:03:25,910
In the future,

44
00:03:25,940 --> 00:03:27,780
if he dares to mistreat you,

45
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:29,240
I'll beat him for you.

46
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:39,220
Mother, you've agreed!

47
00:03:40,530 --> 00:03:42,360
Hurry up and prepare the room.

48
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:45,230
Oh right, remember to find Shi Fa'ke.

49
00:03:46,250 --> 00:03:47,550
You children,

50
00:03:47,570 --> 00:03:49,200
conspiring together on such a rotten plan,

51
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:50,930
all just to get married, right?

52
00:03:51,100 --> 00:03:52,430
Now everything is settled,

53
00:03:52,430 --> 00:03:53,450
so the wedding

54
00:03:53,470 --> 00:03:55,300
should be arranged as soon as possible.

55
00:03:55,300 --> 00:03:56,360
Thank you, Mother.

56
00:03:56,630 --> 00:03:58,160
I'll go prepare right away.

57
00:03:58,420 --> 00:03:59,070
Let's go.

58
00:04:01,250 --> 00:04:01,970
Let go.

59
00:04:02,460 --> 00:04:03,480
You're so clumsy.

60
00:04:04,170 --> 00:04:05,330
I'll take care of Luan'er.

61
00:04:05,330 --> 00:04:07,390
You go handle the important matters.

62
00:04:11,350 --> 00:04:12,690
Lu, I...

63
