I'm sorry.

64
00:04:17,550 --> 00:04:18,839
Did I hurt you?

65
00:04:19,810 --> 00:04:23,020
I don't know how to repay your kindness.

66
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:24,950
You already know?

67
00:04:25,350 --> 00:04:27,270
If you want me to know, I'll know.

68
00:04:27,300 --> 00:04:28,790
If you don't want me to know,

69
00:04:28,790 --> 00:04:30,190
I'll pretend not to know.

70
00:04:30,940 --> 00:04:32,270
But your kindness

71
00:04:32,290 --> 00:04:34,020
will always remain in my heart.

72
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:37,100
