73
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:38,560
It's better if you forget.

74
00:04:38,890 --> 00:04:41,490
Anyway, you still have
one thing to promise me.

75
00:04:42,330 --> 00:04:43,070
I...

76
00:04:46,010 --> 00:04:46,940
Hey, you two,

77
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:48,920
could you stop being all lovey-dovey here?

78
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:49,990
For saving your life,

79
00:04:49,990 --> 00:04:52,390
you should repay him
by becoming his bride.

80
00:04:56,110 --> 00:04:58,930
Qi Shaoheng, stop talking nonsense.

81
00:04:59,260 --> 00:05:00,340
Miss Shi,

82
00:05:01,940 --> 00:05:03,400
how am I talking nonsense?

83
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,890
You two, I'm getting married.

84
00:05:06,050 --> 00:05:07,650
Doesn't it feel like a dream?

85
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:09,610
Miss Shi, shall I pinch you

86
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:11,040
so you can feel it's real?

87
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,320
No need.

88
00:05:14,890 --> 00:05:16,770
It's fortunate that this incident

89
00:05:16,770 --> 00:05:18,830
has led to your marriage with Luan'er,

90
00:05:18,830 --> 00:05:20,740
which is truly a cause for celebration.

91
00:05:20,740 --> 00:05:22,410
However, Lu,

92
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:25,450
didn't you just hire
some porters to put on an act?

93
00:05:25,620 --> 00:05:28,220
Why would they try
to harm us in broad daylight?

94
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:30,240
The Qi family runs an escort agency,

95
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:31,980
so they're bound to have some enemies,

96
00:05:31,980 --> 00:05:33,380
which isn't surprising.

97
00:05:34,750 --> 00:05:36,230
I suppose so.

98
00:05:39,050 --> 00:05:40,390
Anyway,

99
00:05:40,420 --> 00:05:42,080
your marriage is settled now.

100
