Mrs. Qi is very magnanimous,

101
00:05:43,670 --> 00:05:44,750
not blaming us

102
00:05:44,780 --> 00:05:46,150
and even approving your marriage.

103
00:05:46,150 --> 00:05:47,310
Of course.

104
00:05:47,340 --> 00:05:50,670
Thanks to Luan'er
who sacrificed herself to save my mother.

105
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:53,930
Of course, of course.

106
00:05:53,930 --> 00:05:56,320
Miss Shi's brilliant plan

107
00:05:56,350 --> 00:05:57,950
deserves a lot of credit too.

108
00:05:58,890 --> 00:06:00,000
Don't mention it.

109
00:06:00,030 --> 00:06:01,360
I'll never dare think of

110
00:06:01,670 --> 00:06:03,200
such a terrible idea again.

111
00:06:04,410 --> 00:06:05,870
Congratulations, Mr. Qi.

112
00:06:06,230 --> 00:06:08,960
Your luck is indeed excellent.

113
00:06:08,990 --> 00:06:10,880
I see yours isn't bad either.

114
00:06:11,190 --> 00:06:11,920
You...

115
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:18,120
Then I'll trouble you, Miss Shi,

116
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,520
to arrange my wedding as soon as possible

117
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:21,600
with all the proper
betrothal gifts and ceremonies.

118
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,730
Farewell.

119
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,520
Wait, Mr. Qi.

120
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,910
I have a favor to ask of you.

121
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:30,570
Our family

122
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:33,290
has never robbed
your family's silver or valuables.

123
00:06:33,290 --> 00:06:35,390
My parents are
still wrongfully imprisoned.

124
00:06:35,390 --> 00:06:36,710
I know you're a victim,

125
00:06:36,740 --> 00:06:37,940
and so are my parents.

126
00:06:38,130 --> 00:06:38,840
Therefore,

127
00:06:38,860 --> 00:06:41,340
I beg you to go to the Military
Headquarters and tell the truth,

128
00:06:41,340 --> 00:06:43,270
so my parents can be released soon.

129
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:44,960
It's the right thing to do.

130
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:46,150
Those villains today

131
00:06:46,150 --> 00:06:48,130
are likely our family's true enemies.

132
00:06:48,130 --> 00:06:50,700
Miss Shi, you're honest and kind,

133
00:06:50,970 --> 00:06:53,540
and I've also heard
about Ms. Tao's character.

134
00:06:53,540 --> 00:06:55,780
I'll go to the Military Headquarters
right now to plead your case,

135
00:06:55,780 --> 00:06:57,550
and clear your family's name.

136
00:06:58,210 --> 00:06:59,230
Thank you, Mr. Qi.

137
00:06:59,690 --> 00:07:03,690
I'll go get the Information Card
and Betrothal Letter for stamping now.

138
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:13,640
Lu, aren't you going?

139
00:07:16,110 --> 00:07:17,440
Mind your own business.

140
