From now on,

148
00:07:58,890 --> 00:08:02,020
the Agency won't assign
you any more matchmaking cases.

149
00:08:02,300 --> 00:08:04,810
Ms. Deng, you call this old friendship?

150
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:06,220
Don't call me Ms. Deng.

151
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:09,180
Call me Chief Matchmaker Deng.

152
00:08:09,340 --> 00:08:11,740
I am now the Chief Matchmaker
of the Official Matchmaking Agency.

153
00:08:11,740 --> 00:08:12,900
I understand.

154
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:15,370
If the Agency
won't assign me cases, so be it.

155
00:08:15,370 --> 00:08:16,950
That won't stop me.

156
00:08:20,620 --> 00:08:21,340
Master.

157
00:08:22,850 --> 00:08:24,660
Master, as you instructed,

158
00:08:24,950 --> 00:08:26,550
I've brought it for Miss Shi.

159
00:08:28,300 --> 00:08:29,020
Master.

160
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:31,910
I have good news and bad news,

161
00:08:32,010 --> 00:08:34,140
which would you like to hear first?

162
00:08:35,669 --> 00:08:37,169
Would you prefer to speak now,

163
00:08:37,169 --> 00:08:38,370
or never speak again?

164
00:08:39,090 --> 00:08:40,260
Which do you choose?

165
00:08:42,020 --> 00:08:43,020
The good news is,

166
00:08:43,049 --> 00:08:45,450
the Ms. Tao and the Shi father
and son will soon be released from prison.

167
00:08:45,450 --> 00:08:47,120
The bad news is that one

168
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:49,250
says he's being
pressured to marry by court officials,

169
00:08:49,250 --> 00:08:50,520
and has no mood to paint.

170
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:52,020
He ordered you
to keep an eye on Marquis Wu'an,

171
00:08:52,020 --> 00:08:52,920
saying that the Marquis

172
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:54,920
