through the Official Matchmaking Agency.

173
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:57,340
This good news is indeed good news,

174
00:08:57,690 --> 00:08:59,820
but the bad news isn't really that bad.

175
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:03,730
I'll keep a close watch
on the Official Matchmaking Agency.

176
00:09:03,850 --> 00:09:04,890
[A perfect match]

177
00:09:04,310 --> 00:09:05,190
Lu.

178
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:09,910
Fa'ke.

179
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:15,910
[A perfect match]

180
00:09:11,310 --> 00:09:12,770
Look what I bought for you.

181
00:09:13,530 --> 00:09:16,700
Lu, you need to rest well.

182
00:09:18,310 --> 00:09:20,640
Fa'ke, are you facing some trouble again?

183
00:09:21,740 --> 00:09:22,630
Lu.

184
00:09:22,650 --> 00:09:23,890
I have good news,

185
00:09:23,990 --> 00:09:25,170
and bad news.

186
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,130
Which one do you want to hear first?

187
00:09:28,940 --> 00:09:30,240
Whichever you want to tell first,

188
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,490
that's what I want to hear first.

189
00:09:30,980 --> 00:09:35,670
[A perfect match]

190
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,410
Lu.

191
00:09:34,260 --> 00:09:35,860
When my family isn't around,

192
00:09:36,140 --> 00:09:37,390
I've met someone like you

193
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:38,720
who's been so kind to me.

194
00:09:40,180 --> 00:09:41,780
When my parents return,

195
00:09:41,810 --> 00:09:43,250
I'll definitely tell them

196
00:09:43,250 --> 00:09:45,050
about becoming sworn siblings.

197
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,790
I already have a sworn brother,

198
00:09:47,790 --> 00:09:49,520
and don't want another sister.

199
00:09:49,850 --> 00:09:51,150
You don't?

200
00:09:51,750 --> 00:09:54,700
I understand. I'm quite troublesome,

201
00:09:54,790 --> 00:09:56,480
always causing problems

202
00:09:56,790 --> 00:09:58,650
and dragging others into my mess.

203
00:09:59,110 --> 00:10:00,480
Let me remind you

204
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,940
about my hobbies and such.

205
00:10:03,550 --> 00:10:04,710
I remember,

206
00:10:04,740 --> 00:10:07,340
helping others
and joining in the excitement.

207
00:10:07,470 --> 00:10:08,550
Lu, look,

208
00:10:08,830 --> 00:10:12,560
[Information Card]

209
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:10,840
the good news is that

210
00:10:10,870 --> 00:10:12,210
Ms. Deng didn't even look

211
00:10:12,210 --> 00:10:13,690
before stamping the Information Card.

212
00:10:13,690 --> 00:10:15,200
The bad news is also that

213
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:16,640
Ms. Deng didn't even look

214
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:18,490
before stamping the Information Card.

215
00:10:18,490 --> 00:10:21,170
So what's the problem?

216
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:24,030
I've only just realized

217
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:26,340
I've always felt close to her,

218
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,550
but she doesn't feel close to me.

219
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:30,460
I suspect she has ulterior motives

220
00:10:30,460 --> 00:10:31,280
and different intentions,

221
00:10:31,280 --> 00:10:32,940
which is why she agreed so readily.

222
00:10:32,940 --> 00:10:33,890
Do you trust me?

223
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:35,090
Of course I do.

224
00:10:35,110 --> 00:10:36,510
Then go ahead and be the matchmaker.

225
00:10:36,510 --> 00:10:38,110
I'll keep an eye on
Marriage Broker Deng's every move

226
00:10:38,110 --> 00:10:39,230
for you.

227
00:10:40,060 --> 00:10:40,900
Really?

228
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:44,650
Won't it interfere
with your important matters?

229
00:10:44,650 --> 00:10:45,450
Of course not,

230
00:10:45,790 --> 00:10:47,270
your business is my business.

231
00:10:47,270 --> 00:10:47,870
Lu,

232
00:10:48,510 --> 00:10:50,840
what exactly are your important matters?

233
00:10:51,750 --> 00:10:54,610
Eating, drinking,
having fun, and helping others.

234
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:58,120
Never mind.
Tell me when you're ready to talk about it.

235
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,300
I'm coming too.

236
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:02,630
Lu, you should get some rest.

237
00:11:02,630 --> 00:11:04,060
You don't need to accompany me.

238
00:11:04,060 --> 00:11:06,520
This is another
one of my important matters.

239
00:11:10,210 --> 00:11:11,370
Accompanying me?

240
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:17,950
Watching the fun.

241
00:11:25,140 --> 00:11:28,140
What's wrong with me?

242
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:30,520
What am I thinking about?

243
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:33,790
My face must be
as red as a baboon's bottom.

244
00:11:35,220 --> 00:11:36,880
It's all Qi Shaoheng's fault,

245
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:39,860
talking nonsense
about pledging myself to him.

246
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:42,460
I've already given my heart to someone.

247
00:11:42,750 --> 00:11:45,100
Lu and I are just good friends,

248
00:11:46,390 --> 00:11:48,450
I mustn't have these stray thoughts.

249
00:11:50,110 --> 00:11:52,410
[Weiyuan Escort Agency]

250
00:11:52,530 --> 00:11:56,230
[Information Card]

251
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,790
The only daughter of the Liu family

252
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:58,150
was born in the Liu residence
in West City of the capital,

253
00:11:58,150 --> 00:11:59,230
named Luan'er,

254
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:00,720
now 18 years old,

255
00:12:00,900 --> 00:12:02,230
her mother deceased...

256
00:12:02,300 --> 00:12:02,990
That's enough.

257
00:12:02,990 --> 00:12:04,480
Stop reading for now.

258
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:07,790
Mrs. Qi,

259
00:12:08,330 --> 00:12:10,050
are you changing your mind,

260
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:11,600
or have I done something wrong?

261
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:14,150
Mother, why did you stop her reading?

262
00:12:16,380 --> 00:12:18,520
Miss Shi, it's nothing,

263
00:12:18,670 --> 00:12:21,670
but there is one thing
you must help me with.

264
00:12:22,380 --> 00:12:23,810
Madam, please tell me,

265
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,480
if it's within my power,

266
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,960
I will fulfill your wish.

267
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:29,290
After exchanging Information Cards
at the Official Matchmaking Agency,

268
00:12:29,290 --> 00:12:31,290
how soon can the wedding take place?

269
00:12:31,580 --> 00:12:34,670
After exchanging
Information Cards and Betrothal Letter,

270
00:12:34,670 --> 00:12:36,220
both families review the Rite Letter,

271
00:12:36,220 --> 00:12:38,820
prepare the dowry,
select an auspicious date,

272
00:12:38,930 --> 00:12:40,590
then the wedding can proceed.

273
00:12:40,910 --> 00:12:42,320
An auspicious date...

274
00:12:44,040 --> 00:12:46,040
Tomorrow is extremely auspicious.

275
00:12:47,550 --> 00:12:50,020
