570
00:24:15,570 --> 00:24:16,330
Xianxian.

571
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:18,990
These pastries
aren't from the He's Bakery.

572
00:24:18,990 --> 00:24:20,390
Not from the He's Bakery?

573
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:21,920
