574
00:24:21,940 --> 00:24:23,780
someone from outside
has been to our home recently.

575
00:24:23,780 --> 00:24:24,410
Yes.

576
00:24:25,350 --> 00:24:26,510
Who could it be?

577
00:24:27,260 --> 00:24:28,530
Who indeed?

578
00:24:32,480 --> 00:24:33,550
Fa'ke.

579
00:24:35,110 --> 00:24:38,510
I won't be going to
the Official Matchmaking Agency anymore.

580
00:24:39,180 --> 00:24:40,250
From now on,

581
00:24:40,510 --> 00:24:44,270
this ancestral hall and the reputation
of the No.1 matchmaker in the world

582
00:24:44,270 --> 00:24:46,190
will be entrusted to you.

583
00:24:46,500 --> 00:24:48,540
Mother, why is that?

584
00:24:48,570 --> 00:24:50,370
I've already signed a guarantee

585
00:24:51,470 --> 00:24:54,340
that I won't be involved in
the Official Matchmaking Agency's affairs for now.

586
00:24:54,340 --> 00:24:55,720
But don't worry,

587
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:57,200
whatever you do,

588
00:24:57,360 --> 00:24:59,000
I'll always support you.

589
00:24:59,920 --> 00:25:00,590
Mother.

590
00:25:02,360 --> 00:25:04,670
Come, open it and see.

591
00:25:16,030 --> 00:25:18,610
Mother, what's this?

592
00:25:18,640 --> 00:25:20,700
I originally wanted to wait until you

593
00:25:20,780 --> 00:25:21,720
