Mother.

600
00:25:45,510 --> 00:25:48,680
I won't let you down, I promise.

601
00:26:39,100 --> 00:26:41,230
Beautiful! It's really beautiful!

602
00:26:42,150 --> 00:26:43,470
Isn't it beautiful?

603
