624
00:27:36,480 --> 00:27:37,610
and I never heard it.

625
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:41,310
What did I say wrong?

626
00:27:42,410 --> 00:27:43,600
What's the matter?

627
00:27:43,750 --> 00:27:45,280
Your two brothers are here.

628
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:48,480
Oh no, my brothers have bad tempers.

629
00:27:48,510 --> 00:27:49,960
You've trespassed into my family's
backyard in broad daylight.

630
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:51,090
They won't listen to any explanation.

631
00:27:51,090 --> 00:27:52,010
Go away, quickly!

632
00:27:52,010 --> 00:27:52,810
Who are you?

633
00:27:53,210 --> 00:27:54,250
[Hechang Pavilion]

634
00:28:05,210 --> 00:28:07,380
