648
00:28:32,070 --> 00:28:33,800
and rescued me from bad people.

649
00:28:33,820 --> 00:28:35,930
Look at his wounds before you speak!

650
00:28:37,390 --> 00:28:39,350
You got out of prison
but still have to follow rules,

651
00:28:39,350 --> 00:28:40,810
