family matters all alone.

653
00:28:42,820 --> 00:28:43,460
Fa'ke,

654
00:28:44,270 --> 00:28:46,040
your two brothers had no choice,

655
00:28:46,040 --> 00:28:47,170
they didn't mean to.

656
00:28:47,920 --> 00:28:50,020
Did you hear that? Did you hear that?

657
00:28:50,050 --> 00:28:52,050
Lu is still speaking up for you.

658
00:28:53,310 --> 00:28:54,840
It's all Xianxian's fault.

659
00:28:55,680 --> 00:28:57,300
It's all Chongshan's fault.

660
00:28:57,530 --> 00:28:58,660
Chongshan's fault.

661
00:28:59,530 --> 00:29:01,110
I'll let you off today.

662
00:29:02,560 --> 00:29:04,790
Lu, I'm going to the He family now.

663
00:29:04,840 --> 00:29:07,070
Please go to Xibao
Pavilion to invite Ms. Li.

664
00:29:07,070 --> 00:29:09,200
Let's meet at Qi Shaoheng's doorstep.

665
00:29:10,940 --> 00:29:12,750
I can invite Ms. Li too.

666
00:29:14,180 --> 00:29:14,990
Chongshan.

667
00:29:15,020 --> 00:29:17,230
Go to the He family
and bring Ketian to support us.

668
00:29:17,230 --> 00:29:18,970
Alright, I'll go to
the He family right away.

669
00:29:18,970 --> 00:29:19,730
Let's go.

670
00:29:25,090 --> 00:29:26,000
Lu.

671
00:29:26,070 --> 00:29:26,930
Lu.

