You can use that instead.

674
00:29:29,830 --> 00:29:30,760
You two are so...

675
00:29:30,790 --> 00:29:31,310
Okay.

676
00:29:31,330 --> 00:29:31,830
Let go.

677
00:29:31,510 --> 00:29:33,290
[Hechang Pavilion]

678
