683
00:29:46,690 --> 00:29:47,950
Look, look!

684
00:29:52,930 --> 00:29:54,480
So impressive!

685
00:30:08,290 --> 00:30:09,850
For Chongshan's sake,

686
00:30:10,030 --> 00:30:11,480
I've arranged everything for you,

687
00:30:11,480 --> 00:30:13,080
