689
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:17,140
I always knew you were the best.

690
00:30:17,170 --> 00:30:17,920
Thank you.

691
00:30:22,140 --> 00:30:23,650
Ladies and gentlemen,

692
00:30:23,780 --> 00:30:26,070
Miss Luan'er has
specially invited He's Bakery

693
00:30:26,070 --> 00:30:28,030
