697
00:30:38,030 --> 00:30:40,010
How did it become Miss Liu's idea?

698
00:30:40,040 --> 00:30:41,280
What are you up to now?

699
00:30:41,300 --> 00:30:42,380
Well, for a wedding celebration,

700
00:30:42,380 --> 00:30:44,000
