701
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:44,840
Kexian.

702
00:30:44,880 --> 00:30:46,790
I'm inviting you on behalf of Luan'er.

703
00:30:46,790 --> 00:30:48,500
Your family's wedding candies and cakes

704
00:30:48,500 --> 00:30:49,970
