they should praise her generously.

712
00:31:03,960 --> 00:31:05,790
Alright, I'll do as you say.

713
00:31:06,130 --> 00:31:09,220
Kexian, you don't even
ask why before following her orders.

714
00:31:09,220 --> 00:31:11,510
Whatever Fa'ke tells
you to do, you just do it.

715
00:31:11,510 --> 00:31:13,470
Do you have any idea
how much this deal is worth?

716
00:31:13,470 --> 00:31:15,040
