718
00:31:16,140 --> 00:31:17,580
our family business will eventually

719
00:31:17,580 --> 00:31:19,140
be bled dry by Fa'ke.

720
00:31:19,210 --> 00:31:20,350
Ketian.

721
00:31:20,380 --> 00:31:22,400
I've already given you
Chongshan to look after the accounts,

722
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:23,480
