723
00:31:23,480 --> 00:31:26,410
Chongshan volunteered
to help me with the accounts.

724
00:31:30,460 --> 00:31:33,410
[He's Bakery]

725
00:31:33,470 --> 00:31:35,870
Ketian, money isn't as important as Fa'ke.

726
00:31:36,070 --> 00:31:38,130
Whatever she asks me to do, I'll do it.

727
00:31:38,130 --> 00:31:39,600
She must have her reasons,

728
00:31:39,680 --> 00:31:41,350
so why ask so many questions?

729
00:31:43,220 --> 00:31:44,680
