730
00:31:46,290 --> 00:31:47,730
Liu Luan'er, the new
bride of the Qi family,

731
00:31:47,730 --> 00:31:49,130
is treating everyone to pastries.

732
00:31:49,130 --> 00:31:50,970
Come, there's enough for everyone.

733
00:31:50,970 --> 00:31:52,460
Liu Luan'er, I know her.

734
00:31:52,550 --> 00:31:54,200
She's a very gentle girl.

735
00:31:54,220 --> 00:31:55,940
