742
00:32:11,480 --> 00:32:12,510
What is it?

743
00:32:13,460 --> 00:32:15,560
When Mrs. Qi comes out,

744
00:32:15,720 --> 00:32:17,390
please praise Liu Luan'er for me,

745
00:32:17,390 --> 00:32:19,120
and compliment Mrs. Qi as well.

746
00:32:19,120 --> 00:32:21,120
Make sure to keep her in good spirits

747
00:32:21,160 --> 00:32:22,730
so she feels respected.

748
00:32:23,380 --> 00:32:25,170
Miss Shi, don't worry.

749
00:32:25,200 --> 00:32:27,090
I'll do my absolute best.

750
00:32:31,070 --> 00:32:32,200
Come here.

751
00:32:32,740 --> 00:32:34,580
Um, Pan'er,

752
00:32:34,610 --> 00:32:36,550
now that my parents have returned,

753
00:32:36,630 --> 00:32:39,060
if Lu runs a tab at your Xibao Pavilion

754
00:32:39,080 --> 00:32:40,430
and can't pay it off,

755
00:32:40,460 --> 00:32:41,730
please don't give him a hard time.

756
00:32:41,730 --> 00:32:43,930
Come to me instead,
and I'll cover it for him.

757
00:32:43,930 --> 00:32:44,930
Miss Shi,

758
00:32:44,960 --> 00:32:46,350
your eldest brother often helps me

759
00:32:46,350 --> 00:32:48,210
at Xibao Pavilion when he's free.

760
00:32:48,240 --> 00:32:49,720
I'm more than happy to help you.

761
00:32:49,720 --> 00:32:52,180
There's no need
for formalities between us.

762
00:32:57,160 --> 00:32:59,290
