766
00:33:12,350 --> 00:33:14,080
they brought an outsider here.

767
00:33:15,070 --> 00:33:17,870
Though who the real
outsider is remains to be seen.

768
00:33:27,590 --> 00:33:28,110
This...

769
00:33:28,510 --> 00:33:29,110
This...

770
00:33:29,960 --> 00:33:31,020
What's happening?

771
00:33:31,350 --> 00:33:32,940
Why haven't you left to fetch the bride?

772
00:33:32,940 --> 00:33:34,560
I am Shi Fa'ke, marriage broker
