786
00:34:02,060 --> 00:34:03,240
If she receives this gift,

787
00:34:03,240 --> 00:34:05,710
she'll forgo
all the other expensive gifts.

788
00:34:06,070 --> 00:34:08,030
Miss Shi, what does Luan'er want?

789
00:34:08,110 --> 00:34:09,530
I'll get it for her right away.

790
00:34:09,530 --> 00:34:10,989
She wants something else?

791
00:34:11,070 --> 00:34:13,400
Could it be that
Luan'er looks down on my foolish son

792
00:34:13,400 --> 00:34:14,510
