795
00:34:21,800 --> 00:34:24,530
Then she'll pledge
to stay with him until old age.

796
00:34:30,280 --> 00:34:31,380
I knew it!

797
00:34:31,630 --> 00:34:32,510
Liu Luan'er

798
00:34:32,510 --> 00:34:34,969
